Package: wrathos-bundle-codecs
Version: 1.0
Architecture: amd64
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: WrathOS Project <zxd@lunarys.org>
Depends: wrathos-base
Description: WrathOS media codecs bundle
 Installs VLC, FFmpeg, GStreamer plugins and codec libraries
 for full media playback support including H.264, H.265 and AAC.
